sitting right in front of me!

144
00:08:55,875 --> 00:08:57,250
[ZAPP laughs]

145
00:09:05,375 --> 00:09:06,708
[LEO]
Aah!

146
00:09:08,125 --> 00:09:09,125
[ZAPP grunts]

147
00:09:09,208 --> 00:09:10,791
Zapp, are you okay?

148
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:14,041
So some little brat

149
00:09:14,125 --> 00:09:15,458
can see me, huh?

150
00:09:15,541 --> 00:09:17,791
At least you seem
to be the only one.

151
00:09:17,875 --> 00:09:19,416
Hey, Shiboroba,

152
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:22,500
some Johnny on a moped
saw through your illusion.

153
00:09:22,583 --> 00:09:24,958
Don't see how this could
be any good for us, huh?

154
00:09:25,041 --> 00:09:26,458
Seems like too big of a risk

155
00:09:26,541 --> 00:09:29,000
that word of our stock
in trade might get out.

156
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:38,541
Copy that. We study 'em
without killing 'em.

157
00:09:45,958 --> 00:09:46,958
[engine starts]

158
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:52,583
[HLPD OFFICER] Hey, what
happened? Are you okay?

159
00:09:52,666 --> 00:09:54,000
[ZAPP]
It's all up to you now,

160
00:09:54,083 --> 00:09:55,500
she-bitch.

161
00:09:55,583 --> 00:09:59,125
I did the only thing I could.
Let's just hope it works.

162
00:09:59,208 --> 00:10:01,750
That nose of yours
is our best shot.

163
00:10:09,958 --> 00:10:12,333
Damn it! Ugh!

164
00:10:12,416 --> 00:10:14,375
I lost sight of it!

165
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:20,875
[YAHABIO] You look like
a normal earth boy,

166
00:10:20,958 --> 00:10:23,083
but there's more
to you, isn't there?

167
00:10:23,166 --> 00:10:25,833
What about you? Just what
the hell are you freaks up to?

168
00:10:27,875 --> 00:10:29,583
Are these people--

169
00:10:29,666 --> 00:10:31,000
Are they alive?

170
00:10:31,083 --> 00:10:32,458
[YAHABIO]
Well until we eat them.

171
00:10:32,541 --> 00:10:35,583
We've got 'em
vacuum-sealed for freshness.

172
00:10:35,666 --> 00:10:38,458
No way! You know it's
prohibited to eat humans

173
00:10:38,541 --> 00:10:41,375
ever since the Chrysler-Galadona
Accord was passed, right?

174
00:10:41,458 --> 00:10:42,625
And why else do you think

175
00:10:42,708 --> 00:10:45,291
we'd be going to all
this trouble, you idiot?

176
00:10:45,375 --> 00:10:46,916
[SHIBOROBA laughs]

177
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,750
[SHIBOROBA]
What's going on here?

178
00:10:48,833 --> 00:10:50,541
No fighting, you two!

179
00:10:50,625 --> 00:10:52,666
[SHIBOROBA laughs]

180
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:54,416
My friends are never
gonna let you get a--

181
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:57,291
Oh, we'll get away
with it. Why wouldn't we?

182
00:10:57,375 --> 00:10:58,916
You saw through my illusion.

183
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,791
