and just look at the world
of crap you're in now.

186
00:11:07,833 --> 00:11:08,833
Oh, my!

187
00:11:08,916 --> 00:11:11,375
The All-seeing Eyes of the Gods!

188
00:11:11,458 --> 00:11:13,583
[STARPHASE]
Yeah, acknowledged. Don't worry.

189
00:11:13,666 --> 00:11:16,125
It's not your fault. They sound
tricky, but we'll get them.

190
00:11:16,208 --> 00:11:18,000
I mean, I'm guessing they
could cast an illusion

191
00:11:18,083 --> 00:11:20,083
that would fool anybody.

192
00:11:20,166 --> 00:11:22,083
Yeah, so, you know...

193
00:11:22,166 --> 00:11:23,541
how can I say this?

194
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:26,500
Stop crying, Chain!

195
00:11:26,583 --> 00:11:27,958
[GILBERT]
Did they change the vehicle's

196
00:11:28,041 --> 00:11:29,416
make along the way?

197
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:30,666
Hm?

198
00:11:31,708 --> 00:11:32,875
It was an amazing trick

199
00:11:32,958 --> 00:11:35,041
if they fooled the
invisible werewolf.

200
00:11:35,125 --> 00:11:36,958
As for Leo, though,

201
00:11:37,041 --> 00:11:40,041
nothing can get past his eyes.

202
00:11:40,125 --> 00:11:41,375
[STARPHASE]
Oh, man, this has

203
00:11:41,458 --> 00:11:43,083
all the makings of a real mess.

204
00:11:45,250 --> 00:11:47,208
And we better clean it up fast.

205
00:11:47,291 --> 00:11:48,750
[SHIBOROBA]
Ah! What an incredibly

206
00:11:48,833 --> 00:11:50,458
exquisite work of art!

207
00:11:50,541 --> 00:11:52,583
I can barely contain myself!

208
00:11:52,666 --> 00:11:54,291
Let's hurry up and
finish this work here,

209
00:11:54,375 --> 00:11:57,708
so I can immerse myself
in his dissection!

210
00:11:59,458 --> 00:12:01,125
[SHIBOROBA laughs]

211
00:12:14,166 --> 00:12:15,583
[SONIC whimpers]

212
00:12:19,458 --> 00:12:21,833
Ugh. Sonic.

213
00:12:23,125 --> 00:12:24,541
Where are we?

214
00:12:24,625 --> 00:12:26,500
How deep have we gone?

215
00:12:29,416 --> 00:12:31,458
The fog is thick.

216
00:12:31,541 --> 00:12:34,791
If we go any deeper,
it may be hopeless for us.

217
00:12:38,166 --> 00:12:41,541
I've gotta let Klaus and
the others know where we are.

218
00:12:46,083 --> 00:12:46,958
[SONIC squeaks]

219
00:12:48,958 --> 00:12:51,083
It's so embarrassing.

220
00:12:51,166 --> 00:12:54,500
The first sign of trouble
and I go crying to my friends.

221
00:12:56,208 --> 00:13:01,833
It's like nothing about my life
has changed at all, has it?

222
00:13:01,916 --> 00:13:05,208
I have to-- I've gotta get
out of this one on my own.

223
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:10,708
I mean, come on! I'm a
member of Libra now!

224
00:13:16,666 --> 00:13:18,291
What the hell am
I supposed to do?

225
00:13:18,375 --> 00:13:19,875
I'm just a regular guy!

226
00:13:19,958 --> 00:13:22,375
I don't have any
killer skills or powers!

227
00:13:22,458 --> 00:13:23,541
My blood's not a weapon!

228
00:13:23,625 --> 00:13:25,250
I just have these
stupid blue eyes!

229
00:13:25,333 --> 00:13:26,458
[screams]

230
00:13:26,541 --> 00:13:27,416
Eyes?

231
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,458
[CHAIN]
Zapp is the only one

232
00:13:29,541 --> 00:13:30,458
they brought in.

233
00:13:30,541 --> 00:13:32,208
I think we can safely assume

234
00:13:32,291 --> 00:13:34,208
that Leo's probably
been abducted.

235
00:13:34,291 --> 00:13:38,875
Also, you need to hear what
the ER doctor has to say.

236
00:13:38,958 --> 00:13:41,625
There's something not
right about this patient.

237
00:13:41,708 --> 00:13:44,333
To put it mildly, it's
disturbing all of the nurses.

238
00:13:44,416 --> 00:13:46,291
Do you know his
medical history at all?

239
00:13:46,375 --> 00:13:48,708
Anything you can
tell me would help.

240
00:13:48,791 --> 00:13:52,416
Well, as soon as we give him
a transfusion, it disappears.

241
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,958
The blood, I mean.

242
00:13:54,041 --> 00:13:55,750
You did something right, Zapp!

243
00:13:59,666 --> 00:14:00,791
[SONIC squeaks]

244
00:14:00,875 --> 00:14:02,583
[YAHABIO]
Whoa! What's going on?

245
00:14:02,666 --> 00:14:04,583
Why am I seeing a monkey?

246
00:14:04,666 --> 00:14:06,250
[SONIC giggles]

247
00:14:09,333 --> 00:14:11,166
[CHAIN]
Track them using his blood?

248
00:14:11,250 --> 00:14:12,375
[STARPHASE]
That's right.

249
00:14:12,458 --> 00:14:13,666
Zapp's blood's
extending from his body

250
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,291
like a thread from a spindle.

251
00:14:15,375 --> 00:14:17,750
It'll lead us straight
to the vanishing vehicle.

252
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:23,208
That's why the blood
transfusions keep disappearing.

253
00:14:24,375 --> 00:14:26,458
Frankly, it's a
superhuman maneuver.

254
00:14:26,541 --> 00:14:28,208
